{"tid":999919,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"香港球員杜國榆加盟西乙B球隊胡米利亞","createTime":"2019-01-29T05:34:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-29T19:10:29.000Z","uid":9030,"like":110,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"5ced021859a140fe62f476521bb38d26b3cfc2c1","tid":999919,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T05:34:40.000Z","msg":"OFICIAL. Remi, refuerzo para el centro del campo del filial<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uJcOW03.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuJcOW03.png&h=a5facccf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.futbolclubjumilla.es/oficial-remi-refuerzo-para-el-centro-del-campo-del-filial/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.futbolclubjumilla.es%2Foficial-remi-refuerzo-para-el-centro-del-campo-del-filial%2F&d=Osx8LrH6dWr2xFCVFeSzB1zEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=284985d5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.futbolclubjumilla.es/oficial-remi-refuerzo-para-el-centro-del-campo-del-filial/</a>"},{"pid":"88933706ab15180c5fbbe495c9968d4d446535eb","tid":999919,"uid":6435,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T05:35:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88676acd0d425dda4878ae3515d03deedf87405e","tid":999919,"uid":9030,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T05:36:37.000Z","msg":"胡米尼亞現位列西乙B4第9位"},{"pid":"04b94899d5433c92f06364deff4cc87f3a50481a","tid":999919,"uid":3747,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T05:38:45.000Z","msg":"Liga 1|2|3 定 B呀？"},{"pid":"dae4573152f61c2490e03597c9e6e0cf066b0f63","